    trekHighlights: [`Tashi Lapcha Pass at 5,755m with technical glacier crossing`, `Sacred Rolwaling beyul valley of the Nyingma Buddhists`, `Tsho Rolpa glacial lake and climate change frontline`, `Beding and Na villages in pristine alpine setting`, `Gauri Shankar (7,134m) and Melungtse peak views`, `Route connecting to Everest region via Thame`],
