    trekHighlights: [`Shey Phoksundo Lake (Nepal's deepest, 3,611m) in emerald-turquoise`, `Numa La (5,190m) and Baga La (5,170m) high passes`, `Dho Tarap, one of the world's highest inhabited villages`, `Ancient Bon and Buddhist gompas with rare murals`, `Snow leopard and Himalayan wolf habitat`, `Landscape immortalised in The Snow Leopard by Peter Matthiessen`],
    gygQuery: `Dolpo Trek Shey Phoksundo Lake Nepal`,
    bookingCity: `Nepalgunj`,
