    seoDescription: `Discover Birgunj, Nepal's busiest border city and trading hub in Parsa, Madhesh Province. Visit Gandhi Mai Temple, explore vibrant Bihari-Nepali market culture and access Parsa Wildlife Reserve near the India border.`,
