    howToGetThere: `Fly from Kathmandu to Tumlingtar (35 min), then jeep to Chainpur (2-3 hrs). Alternatively, fly to Bhojpur and continue by jeep. Road from Hile via Dhankuta to Chainpur is possible but long. Most visitors combine with a Makalu or Arun Valley trek.`,
